(175, 1, '2018-04-18 13:48:44', '2018-04-18 13:48:44', '<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Poker Sports League Season 2</strong> is underway and is scheduled for May 9th to May 13th in Goa. Season 2 will see 11 city-based teams from across the country competing for a whopping prize money of<strong> INR 3.60 crore</strong>. The teams this year will consist of a total of 10 players each, comprising of one mentor/ playing captain, two pro-players, two from free live qualifiers, three from free online qualifiers and two wild-card entries.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Check out our teams with their full lineup<a href="https://www.pokersportsleague.com/teams"> here</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">After a Press Conference that started with an introduction by Mr. Pranav Bagai, CEO and Co-Founder, Selection Ceremony kicked off with our Brand Ambassador Mr. Vishwananthan Anand unveiling the trophy and sharing a few words about the league.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_172" align="alignnone" width="300"]<img class="size-medium wp-image-172" src="/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/6F8A2548-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /> Mr. Vishwananthan Anand sharing some thoughts on Poker &amp; Chess[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-173" src="/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/6F8A2455-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">At the Team Selection Ceremony which was held on April 15 at the Playboy Club, Delhi, owners and mentors were given the opportunity to choose the best players for their respective team.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">2 players were chosen from Live Qualifiers basis their performance in the live poker tournaments hosted by PSL across India. This was followed by 3 players being chosen from online qualifiers. Both live and online qualifiers were held over a span of 3 months. It took a lot of dedication and time to reach this stage and we are absolutely excited for the league to begin!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>Congratulations to all the selected players and their teams!</strong></p>', 'Team Selection Ceremony Season 2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '153-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-04-18 13:48:44', '2018-04-18 13:48:44', '', 153, 'http://www.pokersportsleague.com/blog/153-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
